Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka Mikoto, who thought her life had returned to normal, is once again disturbed by darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.91,0:00:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious organization is acting around the remains of Tree Diagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Level 4 who uses Move Point, Musujime Awaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Shirai Kuroko, who catches a glimpse into Misaka's lonely battle through her own covert actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:25.43,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,700)\pos(732,486)}#07 Move Point\NCoordinate Movement
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of them are civilians...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like she underestimated my powers, assuming I wouldn't teleport myself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just feel like it, regardless of the trauma...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not called trauma due to the fact that you cannot overcome it so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two years ago, you sustained serious injuries after teleporting yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you perhaps make some sort of mistake during your coordinate calculations and run into a wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, oh my, isn't that pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason to fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I avoided your vital areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully, all I am doing is repeating what you have done to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have this hemostatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It helps to prevent bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you would be so kind as to lay down and treat your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.36,0:01:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once completed, we can consider ourselves even.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be quite fond of Tokiwadai's Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, is she really worth going this far{all this trouble} to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Railgun's{her} selfish yet sentimental dream world worth it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.13,0:02:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Albeit a selfish wish, it is one that Onee-sama desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world where neither one of us interferes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By{a} mere flick of a coin, she could destroy everything in her path if she so desired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Onee-sama is someone who can honestly say that she doesn't want to fight even in deepest despair.{Alas, Onee-sama is one who can honestly say "I wish not to fight," even when depressed.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you truly think that I could just ignore those emotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I am going to have you return her life back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The life that someone, somewhere, dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One that I support.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I trample over those feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll come out the winner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same trick will not work a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot teleport?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in so much pain that you lost your ability to teleport?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you ever heard of this story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Once upon a time, there was a powerful Esper and an organization."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}"The organization believed that, if they could increase the number of powerful Espers, they may gain immense powers."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Many clones were produced."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But the results were horrible."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The little lambs that were created didn't even have a percentage of the original's power."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"They were complete failures."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}"I will now organize what we know so far," says MISAKA-10032 while opening the network, calling out to its many members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Currently, only Academy City has the Remnant necessary to restore Tree Diagram."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The name of the outside organization targeting it is 'Science Society.'"{Asociacion de cienia}{is the Association of Science}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no mistake in that intel, is there?" confirms MISAKA-10032 again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There is certainly no mistake," affirms MISAKA-10044.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But 10032, you sustained a lot more damage than any of the others."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shouldn't you remain in the hospital?" asks MISAKA-10744 worriedly. {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It doesn't matter," replies MISAKA-10032, immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The restoration of Tree Diagram must be prevented at all costs,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,says MISAKA-10032 as she reaffirms her determination, remembering the faces of that boy and girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Understood. It's up to you then," nods MISAKA-14458 in agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We'll leave it to you," agrees MISAKA-19002.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"MISAKA is also counting on you!" says MISAKA says MISAKA while making her request.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No wait, MISAKA wants to do something too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't just stay here and do nothing!" says MISAKA says MISAKA—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you mumbling to yourself for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nothing!" says MISAKA says MISAKA covering her mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shirai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The clones are genetically identical to the original, and even went through the exact same power development training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why didn't the clones reach the same level as the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this mean that there are other factors other than brain structure that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can find those, wouldn't non-humans also be able to use powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only need intelligence on-par, or better than, that of human.{All it takes to bring them to the level of humans is a brain.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer might be closer than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aiming to power-up the machine...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A machine is merely a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it can make a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as we have an ultimate simulating machine that can recreate every possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will investigate every possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can non-humans use Esper powers or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, dolphins are called the humans of the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the society of ants has a rigid set of rules and an order of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Psychic powers may not be limited to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does it have to be humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.70,0:07:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is why I will use this Remnant to create a new Tree Diagram!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm sorry! Please let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Index-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so mean, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went out of the way to think of a tongue-twister too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Touma is a twat that takes tofu from the toilet"... {YAY CREATIVE LIBERTIES. feel free to come up with something better :) }{LOLHAHAHHAHAHAHAHHAHAHA}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, you're just making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just joking...{I mean, good one...}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I have a request," says MISAKA from the bottom of her heart as she faces you directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please save the lives of MISAKA and her sisters."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That experiment...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I won't allow it to start again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Signs of a fight between two Espers in a restaurant in Area F?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.51,0:09:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you, Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for me? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You joined up with an external organization for that sole purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the invaluable Remnant in my possession, I cannot repair it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need an organization with the technology, knowledge, and aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you feel, Shirai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you first gained possession of your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, it was scary for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared of how I could hold such power in my grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't have to come to a human, and certainly didn't have to come to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so why do I have this power?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The children with me harbor the same anguish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They curse their powers and continue to search for answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they did not hesitate to cooperate with me, even if it meant becoming my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it not happened to you as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where you've used your power to hurt someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.44,0:10:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are very much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Shirai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you also wish to know the truth, I'd be more than happy to fill you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:10:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think you could convince me, Shirai Kuroko, with such narcissistic words?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a typical criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything you say is so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Espers may not have needed to become monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a dangerous—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One's power is nothing more than a power, no matter how far it is taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you use your power is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid can you be not to realize something so obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are scared of your own powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not want it because it may hurt someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you have a power or not does not change whether or not you are the type of person who will harm another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are merely stating that you are special and no one else is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are nothing but a corrupted individual with a condescending attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now proceed to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...beat that rotten conviction of yours into shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've destroyed all that I've lived for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were it not for you, I would still have hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maximum weight I can move with my Move Point is 4,520kg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can smash things into this building from a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I can make this building collapse, with you in it!{a building weighs a heckuva lot more than 4 tons, lady}{LOL inorite}{you don't need to move the whole building to destroy it guys... >demolition crews}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You still needed that case?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy you!{can I swear?: I'll fucking kill you!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much like you've killed all that I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to return the favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4,520kg...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This light...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away, Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroko!{what the hell jumping thru rocks?}{touma is a badass}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is A001 calling M000.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my report after confirming the code...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tricking the children and hiding in a safe place to watch the show...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.10,0:15:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be enjoying yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man...{DUN DUN DUN!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took all the trouble to come out here...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what am I presented with? Some third-rate loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accelerator?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Level 5 in Academy City that even the Railgun cannot defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I face someone like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have lost your power on August 31st.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have your calculation ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You no longer have the power you once had!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.42,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So pitiful that I would hug you tight if you were being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I suffered brain damage that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I now perform my calculations externally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that I've gotten weaker doesn't mean that you've gotten any stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless! {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, the road belongs to me, Accelerator!{note: apparently Ippoutsuukou == Accelerator, so this is my attempt to mesh the concept}{From here on, every road you can go down leads to me, Accelerator!}{From here on, you've only got one path: the one towards Accelerator!}{bleeeh idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put your tail between your legs and get your ass back where you came from!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this state, I might be retiring from the title of strongest in Academy City...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that I will at least continue to call myself the strongest in front of that brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally mastered how to buy juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Touma?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "What's wrong?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to pay Shirai a visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I decided to go see Misaka's sister instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what {\i1}was{\i0} the Remnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came out of the building looking all cool with the person who was just naked in your arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.98,0:19:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you didn't actually figure out anything later, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some girl who's apparently the culprit got all beaten up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what was in the case was smashed to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.61,0:19:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, I wonder who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"So I heard that ultimately Yomikawa went outside and destroyed the 'Science Society.'"{Asociacion de cienia}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Apparently they had approached Amai Ao, too{what's this?}," says MISAKA says MISAKA while making a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hey, what's with the lack of enthusiasm?!" says MISAKA says MISAKA—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your appreciation by being quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's weather forecast wasn't accurate either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama, I have realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the place I saw yesterday was none other than your battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.44,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole incident stemmed from my own inexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Onee-sama, please keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will use that smile as energy to get back on my feet once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kuroko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.93,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Daihaseisai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The students are all fired up for the largest event in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a new magician that takes this chance to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her aim is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Daihaseisai."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths, this epic will begin!
